quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  53,45,"Yaha! Achiika! Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun nam (binshɛɣu kam) balibu buyi, ka di nyɛ doo ni paɣa"
  53,46,"Ni maniyyi (dablim kom), bɛ yi ti dulim li bahi na"
  53,47,Yaha! Achiika! Ŋuna n-yɛn ti nam (binnamda) namdi palli (Zaadali)
  53,48,"Yaha! Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun tiri arzichi din galsi, ni din pɔra"
  53,49,"Yaha! Ŋuna n-nyɛ shiɣira Duuma. (Shi’ira nyɛla saŋmari so Ŋun ne pam, ka Maka chεfurinim’ daa jεmdi li)"
  53,50,Yaha! Ŋuna (Naawuni) n-daa niŋ tuuli Aadunim’ (Annabi Hudu niriba) hallaka
  53,51,"Ni Samuudunima (Annabi Salihu niriba), ka daa bi guui so (bɛ puuni)"
  53,52,"Yaha! Pɔi ni bana, (O daa min niŋ) Annabi Nuhu niriba hallaka. Achiika! Bana n-daa gari sokam zualinsi dibu, ka kpahiri yεɣiri targa n-gari sokam"
  53,53,Ni ninvuɣu shεba bɛ ni daa lebi bɛ tiŋgbani pili (Annabi Lutu niriba)
  53,54,Ka din daa liri ba (azaaba) maa daa liri ba
  53,55,"Dinzuɣu, (yaa nyini ninsala)! A Duuma (Naawuni) yolisigu dini ka a leei zilsira"
  53,56,"Ŋumbɔŋɔ (Annabi Muhammadu) maa nyɛla saɣisigulana, ka o nyɛla ŋun be kurumbuni nima ban tiri saɣisigu la puuni"
  53,57,Din miri maa (Chiyaama yiɣisibu) miri ya na
  53,58,Di ka ŋun yɛn tooi taɣi li ka pa ni Naawuni
  53,59,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, yɛtɔɣali (Al-Kur’aani) ŋɔ maa ka yi niŋdi lahiʒiba"
  53,60,"Ka yi lara, ka bi kuhira"
  53,61,Ka nyɛla ban kpɛrita
  53,62,"Tɔ! Ŋmiɛm ya gbiɛɣu n-ti Naawuni, ka jεm ya O"
  54,1,"Saha (Chiyaama yiɣisibu) miri ya, dinzuɣu ka goli tahibɔɣi (ka pirigi buyi)"
  54,2,"Yaha! Bɛ (Maka chεfurinim’) yi nya yɛlikpahindili, ka bɛ lebi biri ka yεli: “Ŋɔ maa nyɛla sihira din kuli beni sahakam.”"
  54,3,"Ka bɛ labsi li (Alkur’aani aayanim’) ʒiri, ka doli bɛ suhuyurlim. Amaa! yɛllikam mi nyɛla din dihitabli"
  54,4,Yaha! Achiika! Lahibaya kaba na di (Alkur’aani) puuni din nyɛ tahigu
  54,5,"Di (Alkur’aani) nyɛla yɛmgoliŋga din paai tariga, amaa! Valsigu (wa’azu) bi niŋdi (ninsalinim’) anfaani shεli"
  54,6,"Dinzuɣu (Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yim bɛ yɛla ni, dabsi’ shεli beni ka mololana so (Malaaika Israafilu) yɛn ti moli n-zaŋ chaŋ binshɛɣu bɛ (ninsalinim’) ni je"